          <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mt-3 text-[15px]" style="max-width:70ch;">None of them is exotic or expensive on its own; the magic is in doing all of them, consistently, for decades. Here are the longevity practices we build into every C.A.Gs Grey before it goes home, and that we coach every family to continue.</p>
