          <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed text-[15px]" style="max-width:70ch;">A bird eating a balanced <a href="/african-grey-parrot-diet/">pellet-and-vegetable diet</a> with calcium and vitamin-A support, weighed weekly and seen by a vet each year, has already cleared the biggest hurdles to a six-decade life.</p>
