        <p class="font-sora text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mx-auto text-center mt-8" style="max-width:70ch;">Lifespan is the headline, but the day-to-day is where a long life is won — our <a href="/african-grey-parrot-care-guide/">full African Grey care guide</a> covers housing, enrichment, and lighting, our <a href="/african-grey-parrot-diet/">diet guide</a> details the feeding that adds years, and our <a href="/african-grey-parrot-guide/">complete African Grey guide</a> walks first-time owners through what to expect across a Grey's decades.</p>
